-Thank you, Ms. Tanner.
-Thank you. Thank you.

1204
01:08:05,047 --> 01:08:06,982
Erik.

1205
01:08:07,015 --> 01:08:09,151
That's a little suspicious.

1206
01:08:09,184 --> 01:08:11,987
This is weird. How did she
know? And why did she pick

