You've seen what happened to Naudi.

1274
01:11:27,115 --> 01:11:30,652
It's most likely that the
killer has been here before.

1275
01:11:30,685 --> 01:11:32,220
Hell,

1276
01:11:32,254 --> 01:11:34,022
