happen to her sooner or later.

1286
01:12:03,485 --> 01:12:05,353
So...

1287
01:12:05,387 --> 01:12:08,189
until the killer is found,

1288
01:12:08,223 --> 01:12:11,293
let's try to prioritize

1289
01:12:11,326 --> 01:12:14,262
